OL,5, A woman who stabbed her lodger to death
OL,6, has been jailed for life, with a       
OL,7, minimum term of 20 years.              
OL,9,FYoga teacher Dawn Lewis, 54, stabbed   
OL,10,FGlenn Richards, 61, on the evening of  
OL,11,F18 April at her cottage in Glastonbury,
OL,12,Fafter their relationship had           
OL,13,Fdeteriorated.                          
OL,15,FOn Thursday a jury found her guilty of 
OL,16,Fhis murder by an 11-1 majority verdict.
OL,18,FSentencing her on Friday, Judge William
OL,19,FHart said Mr Richards had died in a    
OL,20,F"savage attack" that Lewis had planned.
